# A message before we start:
# #######################################
# CaviR Statistics is a free online interactive web application created to overcome statistical difficulties by only selecting the relevant variables. 
# The goal is to make the language 'R' applicable to data analyses for researchers,
# especially those who don't have time or don't feel urged to learn the R language. 
# Moreover, CaviR Statistics saves researchers' time in analyses and visualizations of their data. 
# We don't want to create a new blackbox software like SPSS, rather a free open source application 
# which researchers can use to visualize and to think of their data in a more conscious way.
# By making this open source, I, Joachim, hope more people are interested in extending the number of functions in CaviR Statistics.
# 
# Take care and enjoy Cavir! 
# If you have any questions or wish for more information, don't hesitate to contact me.
# 
# Joachim
